  <!-- Introduction Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-background">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-display font-bold text-text mb-6">
          What Are Email Reminders?
        </h2>
        <div
          class="prose prose-lg max-w-none space-y-6 text-text-muted leading-relaxed"
        >
          <p>
            Email reminders are automated notifications sent to appointment
            attendees before their scheduled meetings. Instead of manually
            sending reminder emails or relying on attendees to remember
            appointments on their own, email reminder systems automatically send
            perfectly timed messages that reduce no-shows and improve attendance
            rates. CalendHub's email reminder feature sends customizable
            reminder sequences based on your configured timing, ensuring every
            attendee receives timely notifications before their appointments.
          </p>

          <p>
            No-shows cost businesses billions annually in lost revenue and
            wasted time. Studies show that automated email reminders reduce
            no-show rates by 60-80% compared to appointments without reminders.
            The key is timing and repetition: a single reminder 24 hours before
            an appointment is effective, but a sequence of reminders
            (confirmation at booking, 24-hour reminder, 2-hour final reminder)
            dramatically improves attendance. CalendHub automates this entire
            process, sending reminder emails based on your custom schedule
            without any manual intervention required.
          </p>

          <p>
            Unlike manual reminder systems that require staff to send individual
            emails or remember to contact attendees, automated email reminders
            work 24/7 in the background. When someone books an appointment
            through your CalendHub scheduling page, the reminder sequence starts
            automatically. The system calculates reminder timing based on the
            appointment date and your configured schedule, then sends emails at
            precisely the right moments. This automation saves hours of
            administrative work while ensuring consistent, professional
            communication with every attendee.
          </p>

          <p>
            CalendHub's email reminder system integrates directly with your
            calendar and scheduling workflow. Reminders include all appointment
            details, calendar file attachments for easy adding to personal
            calendars, and one-click reschedule or cancel links if plans change.
            You control the message content, timing, sender information, and
            branding to create reminder emails that match your business
            identity. The system tracks delivery, handles timezone conversions
            automatically, and ensures reminders reach attendees at appropriate
            local times regardless of geographic location.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

